title Dynamic View: Task Management\nLuồng tìm kiếm User qua OpenFeign

actor <<Person>>\nUser as User
participant <<Container>>\nUI as UI
participant <<Container>>\nAPI Gateway as API Gateway
participant <<Container>>\nTask Service as Task Service
participant <<Container>>\nAuthentication Service as Authentication Service
participant <<Container>>\nProfile Service as Profile Service

User->UI: 1. Gõ keyword (email/name)
UI->API Gateway: 2. GET /api/tasks/search-users
API Gateway->Task Service: 3. Forward request
Task Service->Authentication Service: 4. Fetch Auth info (Feign Client)
Task Service->Profile Service: 5. Fetch Profile info (Feign Client)
